" />"},{"pid":"a97c608b6da2caebdc705b03020279ab1cb74b68","tid":2186936,"uid":173326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:56:22.000Z","msg":"佢話支那檢疫隊有經驗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af0d9e841236eb17504b6603fd51508b4959f122","tid":2186936,"uid":62431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc66315f753843551b69bc3c6eeabebf2561b881","tid":2186936,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:19:27.000Z","msg":"佢戴晒頭盔<br />\n<br />\n係講&quot;願意檢測的市民&quot;去做<br />\n唔係話所有市民應該去做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:58:09.000Z","msg":"冇計啦樓豬唔明㗎啦"},{"pid":"6f1d82fd8b3a3089e4a2e73f82f7cbb24e823e90","tid":2186936,"uid":108757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc66315f753843551b69bc3c6eeabebf2561b881","tid":2186936,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:19:27.000Z","msg":"佢戴晒頭盔<br />\n<br />\n係講&quot;願意檢測的市民&quot;去做<br />\n唔係話所有市民應該去做"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:00:42.000Z","msg":"報咗名嘅先去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80926f326ad0cabdfbe1743f7a27e24b2bfce910","tid":2186936,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"af0d9e841236eb17504b6603fd51508b4959f122","tid":2186936,"uid":62431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dc66315f753843551b69bc3c6eeabebf2561b881","tid":2186936,"uid":269629,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:19:27.000Z","msg":"佢戴晒頭盔<br />\n<br />\n係講&quot;願意檢測的市民&quot;去做<br />\n唔係話所有市民應該去做"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:58:09.000Z","msg":"冇計啦樓豬唔明㗎啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:51:24.000Z","msg":"政府專家顧問、港大微生物學系講座教授袁國勇表示，目前透過普及社區檢測計劃找出的陽性個案好像很少，<strong>但少量患者足以令整套防疫措施變得失敗，認為計劃值得推行。</strong>尤其當局已開始放寬一些防疫措施，認為不應再辯論計劃的成本效益問題。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇表示，檢測計劃有另一好處，可讓其他國家看到香港已盡力防疫，有利於討論出入境互通，對香港經濟及很多人的生計影響很大，無人會強迫市民參與檢測，但既然現時有這機會就應利用。他又說，登記人數未及100萬，但假如單日確診個案回升至數十宗，可能會有更多人想檢測。<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇下午聯同行政會議成員林正財，到設於皇仁書院的社區檢測中心視察。袁國勇見記者時親身示範各種採樣方式，自己替自己採樣。他說每種方式都可以，最重要是做法正確。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/latest-news.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Flatest-news.htm&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hco9o6IkP5%2Bxjkbf63jgWy4%3D&h=9fb4c119\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Flatest-news.htm&h=d299e956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/latest-news.htm</a><br />\n點兜好?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c096611b190f5ad148a3014c1422709c381759a9","tid":2186936,"uid":290118,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T11:53:55.000Z","msg":"🥱不了"}]}